      "chinese": "早期族人不懂節育，一個接一個地生孩子，難產、夭折頻生。當時助產士幫忙接生，教導常識，增加了新生兒的存活率，保障產婦平安，有不容小覷的重責大任。",
      "ab": "ku igayganeana kai mapapangale kadruwa ka wathingale ngikakelrete ngiaedeke ku atulalaka, waedeede hemede tulalake, ku pakakucingalre tulalake, ku ngwalredelreda latakalra tuhamuhu, ikai inya zidai kwani, kai tahapatulalaalake ka lasangbasange, palribulu patulalake, wabulru ku apapulringava lu tulalaka, ngwalai ku akivalaa ku ngwalredelreda, ngwalai ku akasahwata ki twalalake, kadruwa ka atulyapapadha ka atwatumana.",
